mods.abstract: The California Magazine of Western Square and Round Dancing by the Square Dancers of Southern California. This edition includes a table of contents which lists the following: "From the Floor", "Square Dance Datebook", "On the Record", "As I See It", "Gold Ribbon Report: -Round Dance Leaders Associations, -Round Dancing-Favorites or Basics", "Teaching Rounds to Square Dancers by Dottie & Jules Billard", "National Convention News", "How Solid Is Your Foundation? by Madeline Allen", "The Dancers Walkthru", "Profile: A University Square Dance Club", "Style Lab: Interrupted Right & Left Grand", "Round the World of Square Dancing", "Workshop", "Caller of the Month: Ralph McMullen", "Current Best Sellers", and "Feature Fashion".
